#include<stdio.h>
double sqrt(double);
int main()
{
 int t,l,u,cnt,found,sum,i,j,n;
 scanf("%d",&t);
 while(t--)
 {
  scanf("%d%d",&l,&u);
  cnt=0;
  for(i=l;i<=u;i++)
  { n=i;
    sum=0;
   while(n)
   { sum+=n%10;
     n/=10;
   }
   found=0;
   if(sum>1)
   { found=1;
    for(j=2;j<=floor(sqrt(sum));j++)
     { if(sum%j==0)
       { found=0;
         break; }
     } }
  if(found)
  cnt++;
 }
 printf("%d\n",cnt);
}
return 0;
}
